<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-tw">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pace.minimal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><%= title %></a>
            </div>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbar-collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li><a href="/">Post</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:;">Donate</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://fb.com/<%= fanpageId %>" target="_blank">Facebook</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    
    
    
    
    <div class="my-container">
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <h1><%= title %></h1>
            <p class="uppercase"><%= shortTitle %></p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="panel-heading">相關設定</div>
        <div class="setting">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <label>
                    <input name="mode" id="ModePhoto" value="photo" type="radio" checked="checked">圖片模式（字數限制：300字）
                </label>
                <br/>
                <label>
                    <input name="mode" id="ModeMessage" value="message" type="radio">純文字模式（字數限制：1024字）
                </label>
            </div>
            
            
            
            
            
            <div id="PhotoPartA" class="col-md-6">
                <div class="text-right col-md-3">主題</div>
                <select class="col-md-9" id="Theme">
                    <% for(var st in Themes) { %>
                        <option value="<%= st %>"><%= Themes[st].name %></option>
                    <% } %>
                </select>
                <br/>
                <div class="text-right col-md-3">字體</div>
                <select class="col-md-9" id="FontFamily">
                    <% for(var sf in Fonts) { %>
                        <option value="<%= sf %>"><%= sf %></option>
                    <% } %>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>


        <br/>
        
        
        <div class="panel-heading">輸入靠北文</div>
        <textarea id="Message" class="col-md-12 message-textarea" placeholder="快快寫個靠北文" rows="7"></textarea>
        
        
        <br/>
        
        
        <div id="PhotoPartB">
            <div class="panel-heading">預覽 - <a class="href-main" id="Redraw" href="javascript:;">重繪</a></div>
            <img id="PhotoReview" class="photo-review" src="" alt="繪圖中" />
            
            
            
            <br/>
        </div>
        
        
        
        <div class="panel-heading">以下規則請遵守 - 參考<a class="href-main" target="_blank" href="https://fb.com/kobeengineer">靠北工程師</a></div>
        <div class="main-rule-privacy">
            1.當你勾選後，即代表您同意遵守 Facebook 社群使用規則.<br/>
            2.嚴禁發表任何霸凌內容、或有相關意圖之內容，違反將被刪除<br/>
            3.靠北勿指名道姓、透漏任何個資或隱私資訊<br/>
            4.嚴禁發表任何情色、暴力之相關內容，或有相關意圖之內容，違反將被刪除<br/>
            5.與本版主題無關、或發文內容明顯為測試意圖、或無關之推薦文、廣告文、職缺文，將被刪除
        </div>
            
        
        
